@host = http://localhost/simple_api

### Hello World
GET {{host}}/hello-world

### List all users
GET {{host}}/users

### Get a user by ID
GET {{host}}/users/1

### Create a new user
POST {{host}}/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "user_name": "John Doe",
    "user_email": "john@example.com",
    "user_password": "secret123"
}

### Update a user
PUT {{host}}/users/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "user_name": "Jane Doe"
}

### Delete a user (soft delete)
DELETE {{host}}/users/1
